// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0059 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 45dd2e38-628e-5d04-bf0b-a43a0d6205a6

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
